00:14:46,215 --> 00:14:49,355
Being new to Xizhou, where can she find
so many people to help her transcribe?

250
00:14:49,355 --> 00:14:50,375
And these characters,

251
00:14:50,375 --> 00:14:53,295
You can tell they're written by an expert
by looking,

252
00:14:53,295 --> 00:14:54,935
Perhaps neither you nor I could write them,

253
00:14:56,775 --> 00:14:58,255
I may not even be able to write it,

254
00:14:59,495 --> 00:15:00,775
They're not by written,

255
00:15:00,775 --> 00:15:01,975
You're joking with me,

256
00:15:01,975 --> 00:15:03,495
Not by written?

257
00:15:03,495 --> 00:15:05,035
Or do they just come out of the air?

258
00:15:05,035 --> 00:15:07,015
Printed,

259
00:15:07,015 --> 00:15:07,575
Give me your hand,

260
00:15:09,455 --> 00:15:13,855
Just like this, printed one by one,

261
00:15:15,815 --> 00:15:17,335
Print,

262
00:15:17,335 --> 00:15:18,435
That's not right either,

263
00:15:18,435 --> 00:15:21,415
Printing so many of them
must be quite time-consuming,

264
00:15:21,415 --> 00:15:23,712
And where would you find so many gems?

265
00:15:23,712 --> 00:15:25,553
It's not gemstone, It's wood,

266
00:15:26,375 --> 00:15:29,055
If one were to make thousands of copies
with wood at one time,

267
00:15:29,055 --> 00:15:31,155
not only would it save time
compared to handwriting,

268
00:15:31,155 --> 00:15:32,655
but it could also be reused,

269
00:15:32,655 --> 00:15:34,775
It's a great method with myriad of benefits,

270
00:15:38,455 --> 00:15:40,695
It seems that I really underestimated
Pei Xingjian,

271
00:15:40,695 --> 00:15:43,415
However, it was that Kudi Liuli
who thought of this idea,

272
00:15:45,735 --> 00:15:48,975
Are you worried that Qu Chongyu'll find out
it was my idea for the engraved boards?

273
00:15:50,495 --> 00:15:53,775
I'm afraid in the next couple of days,
he'll find reasons to test you

274
00:15:54,615 --> 00:15:55,975
If I don't let you take the lead,

275
00:15:55,975 --> 00:15:58,375
that would clearly show
I fear that he might harm you,

276
00:15:58,375 --> 00:15:59,975
But if I do let you take the lead,

277
00:16:00,735 --> 00:16:02,055
I truly cannot be at ease,

278
00:16:03,015 --> 00:16:04,455
Could he possibly murder me to silence me,

279
00:16:05,015 --> 00:16:06,695
or stop at nothing to harm me?

280
00:16:07,775 --> 00:16:10,495
For now, it is not necessary to kill you
to silence you,

281
00:16:11,135 --> 00:16:13,315
He will probe the truth and falsehood
in your words,

282
00:16:13,315 --> 00:16:14,535
seeking to understand your details and motives,

283
00:16:16,055 --> 00:16:17,855
This is better than murder,

284
00:16:17,855 --> 00:16:20,115
But if he really understands Liuli's motives,

285
00:16:20,115 --> 00:16:22,155
will he consider her as a threat

286
00:16:22,155 --> 00:16:23,175
and actually do something to harm her?

287
00:16:27,135 --> 00:16:31,255
In that case, please bring Sanniang over,

288
00:16:33,135 --> 00:16:34,855
Okay, I'm going right away,

289
00:16:40,455 --> 00:16:42,875
If that's the case, you can rest assured,

290
00:16:42,875 --> 00:16:45,415
I have my ways
to keep him from probing further,

291
00:16:46,375 --> 00:16:48,815
Liuli, you must not be overconfident,

292
00:16:48,815 --> 00:16:51,055
Qu Chongyu's intelligence is not inferior
to mine,

293
00:16:51,055 --> 00:16:52,575
And this time he has come prepared,

294
00:16:53,255 --> 00:16:54,375
I'm worried he might be harmful to you,

295
00:16:54,975 --> 00:16:56,835
Just set your heart at ease,

296
00:16:56,835 --> 00:16:59,735
I've got quite a few insights
on dealing with that crazy peacock,

297
00:17:02,495 --> 00:17:04,615
Alright, your wife is so smart,

298
00:17:04,615 --> 00:17:06,015
What else do you have to worry about?

299
00:17:14,975 --> 00:17:17,815
Sister, if Qu Chongyu comes to ask you
about the Buddhist scriptures,

300
00:17:17,815 --> 00:17:19,104
please answer him this way,

301
00:17:48,255 --> 00:17:49,295
<i>It's in his hand as expected,</i>

302
00:17:51,895 --> 00:17:55,215
I got some routine matters to taken care of,
Sorry for keeping Master An waiting,

303
00:17:56,455 --> 00:17:58,415
Minister Qu,

304
00:17:58,415 --> 00:18:00,655
Do you recognize this?

305
00:18:01,215 --> 00:18:03,355
This's the newly made Buddha scripture
by my An family,

306
00:18:03,355 --> 00:18:04,935
Of course I recognize it,

307
00:18:04,935 --> 00:18:06,335
You're indeed a straightforward person,

308
00:18:07,015 --> 00:18:10,095
Can anything here in Xizhou
ever be concealed from Minister Qu?

309
00:18:10,655 --> 00:18:13,775
Besides, the production of the scriptures
in my establishment is all aboveboard,

310
00:18:13,775 --> 00:18:15,015
So why the need to avoid others?

311
00:18:16,575 --> 00:18:17,655
Then come in and speak,

312
00:18:26,175 --> 00:18:27,915
I'm quite fond of this Buddhist scripture,

313
00:18:27,915 --> 00:18:30,095
I just don't know the method of production,

314
00:18:30,615 --> 00:18:32,935
And I don't know how it was made so neatly,

315
00:18:34,175 --> 00:18:35,695
The matter is quite simple really,

316
00:18:35,695 --> 00:18:37,895
You just need to engrave the characters
out of the wood board,

317
00:18:37,895 --> 00:18:39,295
Then apply ink and press it onto the paper,

318
00:18:40,335 --> 00:18:41,695
I've thought of this too,

319
00:18:42,495 --> 00:18:45,575
It's just that I've tried using a wood board
these past two days,

320
00:18:45,575 --> 00:18:47,175
However, I can never find the knack,

321
00:18:47,775 --> 00:18:49,995
How do you carve the characters
in reverse on the wood board?

322
00:18:49,995 --> 00:18:53,215
And what kind of wood board
can withstand the engraving and ink erosion?

323
00:18:53,935 --> 00:18:54,975
Can you please tell me?

324
00:18:56,975 --> 00:18:58,400
Well…

325
00:19:00,895 --> 00:19:01,975
You can surely rest assured,

326
00:19:02,615 --> 00:19:05,095
I'm just curious,

327
00:19:08,735 --> 00:19:11,575
Thus, if you confess honestly,

328
00:19:12,135 --> 00:19:13,695
how about I reward you with a hundred gold?

329
00:19:15,375 --> 00:19:17,024
A hundred gold?

330
00:19:21,775 --> 00:19:23,175
You don't need to worry,

331
00:19:23,775 --> 00:19:25,415
Even if I know the method of production,

332
00:19:25,415 --> 00:19:28,875
I will absolutely not involve myself
in the business of the Buddhist scripture,

333
00:19:28,875 --> 00:19:31,255
With this said,
you can always rest assured, right?

334
00:19:32,375 --> 00:19:34,355
Since the Minister has put it out this way,
there's not much more to say,

335
00:19:34,355 --> 00:19:37,175
If I were to decline further,
it would indeed be quite ungracious,

336
00:19:38,095 --> 00:19:42,915
But the inventor of this engraved board
printing technique is actually my sister,

337
00:19:42,915 --> 00:19:45,415
As for how it's made, I truly have no idea,

338
00:19:47,175 --> 00:19:48,615
Very well then, In that case,

339
00:19:48,615 --> 00:19:52,215
please trouble Master An to go back
and discuss thoroughly with Lady Kudi,

340
00:19:52,935 --> 00:19:54,175
I shall await the good news,

341
00:20:12,055 --> 00:20:15,904
<i>Respect and Honor One's Origin</i>

342
00:20:20,975 --> 00:20:22,304
Say yes to him,

343
00:20:22,855 --> 00:20:25,015
The technique of engraved board
is truly a shortcut to profit,

344
00:20:25,015 --> 00:20:26,655
Is one hundred gold too little?

345
00:20:26,655 --> 00:20:28,855
Actually,
the key to this matter is not complicated

346
00:20:28,855 --> 00:20:31,355
It's just that they didn't think of
using fabric printing skills,

347
00:20:31,355 --> 00:20:32,615
The wooden board we use

348
00:20:32,615 --> 00:20:34,775
was pear wood which first soaked
for several months

349
00:20:34,775 --> 00:20:36,515
at the fabric printing store
before dried thoroughly,

350
00:20:36,515 --> 00:20:38,695
It's much more resilient than ordinary wood,

351
00:20:38,695 --> 00:20:41,395
When carving characters,
there would be no cracks or breaks on it,

352
00:20:41,395 --> 00:20:44,655
The stencil characters are also written
on the special thin paper used at the store,

353
00:20:44,655 --> 00:20:45,815
This way, the reverse side can also

354
00:20:45,815 --> 00:20:47,875
clearly show the handwriting,

355
00:20:47,875 --> 00:20:50,295
These tow thoughts might not
immediately occur to others,

356
00:20:50,295 --> 00:20:51,975
However, that doesn't mean no one would never
be able to figure it out in their lifetime,

357
00:20:52,615 --> 00:20:55,095
There are many skilled artisans
at the crazy peacock's place,

358
00:20:55,095 --> 00:20:57,015
Sooner or later, they will figure these out,

359
00:20:57,015 --> 00:20:59,295
By then, I'm afraid even a hundred gold pieces
would not be obtainable

360
00:20:59,935 --> 00:21:01,255
It's just that by doing so,

361
00:21:01,255 --> 00:21:03,955
Qu Chongyu will definitely ask you
to go to his workshop,

362
00:21:03,955 --> 00:21:05,715
Aren't we falling into his trap?

363
00:21:05,715 --> 00:21:07,235
Sister, there is no need to worry,

364
00:21:07,235 --> 00:21:09,735
Even if he doesn't ask, I will go by myself,

365
00:21:09,735 --> 00:21:10,895
Why is that?

366
00:21:10,895 --> 00:21:12,455
If we don't let him understand clearly,

367
00:21:12,455 --> 00:21:14,255
how can we make him let down his guard?

368
00:21:17,055 --> 00:21:18,895
Then I will go speak with Qu Chongyu,

369
00:21:32,655 --> 00:21:33,895
My lady, watch your step,

370
00:21:40,135 --> 00:21:41,600
Please, this way, My lady

371
00:21:50,695 --> 00:21:52,255
Sorry for the bother, My lady,

372
00:21:52,255 --> 00:21:53,935
No need for formalities, Minister,

373
00:21:53,935 --> 00:21:55,915
Since I have received
your hundred pieces of gold,

374
00:21:55,915 --> 00:21:59,455
even if it's troublesome,
I have no choice but to take this journey

375
00:21:59,455 --> 00:22:01,495
in order to clear your doubts,

376
00:22:01,495 --> 00:22:04,635
I greatly admire your boundless ideas, my lady,

377
00:22:04,635 --> 00:22:06,755
It's just that some details
are still not fully comprehended,

378
00:22:06,755 --> 00:22:08,335
Hope you wouldn't hesitate to enlighten me,

379
00:22:08,335 --> 00:22:09,835
You're being too polite,

380
00:22:09,835 --> 00:22:11,195
Minister's inquiries are meticulous,

381
00:22:11,195 --> 00:22:13,055
I don't quite understand the questions either,

382
00:22:13,055 --> 00:22:14,215
Thank you for your efforts, Lady Kuli,

383
00:22:14,215 --> 00:22:15,815
No worries,

384
00:22:15,815 --> 00:22:17,955
I took your money for it,

385
00:22:17,955 --> 00:22:20,055
After all, they are so generous,

386
00:22:21,135 --> 00:22:23,915
You said these wood pieces
need to be soaked for several months,

387
00:22:23,915 --> 00:22:25,895
They can only be used
after being thoroughly dried,

388
00:22:25,895 --> 00:22:28,455
Just now, Master An brought over a piece,
and the wood is really good,

389
00:22:28,455 --> 00:22:30,095
But I wonder why?

390
00:22:30,935 --> 00:22:33,975
As for why, how could I know?

391
00:22:34,935 --> 00:22:36,655
My lady, are you trying to fob us off?

392
00:22:37,935 --> 00:22:39,755
What does this mean, Prefect Wang?

393
00:22:39,755 --> 00:22:41,055
According to Master An,

394
00:22:41,055 --> 00:22:44,055
the engraved board printing technique
was Lady Kudi's idea,

395
00:22:44,055 --> 00:22:47,255
Well, if that's the case,
how could you not know the production process?

396
00:22:47,255 --> 00:22:49,855
Could it be that someone else
came up with this idea?

397
00:23:01,335 --> 00:23:03,855
Are you saying that I pretend to understand
when I don't

398
00:23:04,495 --> 00:23:06,215
to swindle your money, Prefect Wang?

399
00:23:06,215 --> 00:23:07,295
I misspoke,

400
00:23:07,295 --> 00:23:10,395
I although even though
Lady Kudi came from commoner background,

401
00:23:10,395 --> 00:23:12,215
but you're respected as kin to an official,

402
00:23:12,215 --> 00:23:15,275
you wouldn't resort to such despicable means,

403
00:23:15,275 --> 00:23:17,655
Prefect Wang, you seem to have been sleeping
too well recently,

404
00:23:18,295 --> 00:23:20,335
That's why you're spouting nonsense here,

405
00:23:21,295 --> 00:23:23,535
I really don't know

406
00:23:23,535 --> 00:23:24,855
the reason
why these soaked wooden boards are better,

407
00:23:25,535 --> 00:23:28,175
I only know about all the carving boards
in the fabric printing store

408
00:23:28,735 --> 00:23:31,735
need to be treated in this way
before they can be used,

409
00:23:32,255 --> 00:23:34,455
Otherwise, it is easy to burr during carving,

410
00:23:34,455 --> 00:23:36,915
This is something that everyone would know
in the fabric printing store,

411
00:23:36,915 --> 00:23:39,335
As for the truth in it, who will care?

412
00:23:41,255 --> 00:23:43,775
Fabric printing store?

413
00:23:43,775 --> 00:23:44,935
Of course, fabric printing store,

414
00:23:45,615 --> 00:23:46,695
Minister, you didn't know

415
00:23:46,695 --> 00:23:49,335
that I once worked as a painter
in a fabric printing store,

416
00:23:49,335 --> 00:23:51,235
I'm familiar with craving boards
and dying cloth,

417
00:23:51,235 --> 00:23:53,595
I thought
since the wood engraved board could dye cloth,

418
00:23:53,595 --> 00:23:54,895
there's a great chance that
they could be used for printing books,

419
00:23:55,535 --> 00:23:58,055
Unexpectedly,
it turned out to be the case when tested,

420
00:23:58,775 --> 00:24:01,875
The wood used for engraved boards this time
was indeed from the fabric printing store,

421
00:24:01,875 --> 00:24:03,575
If it hadn't been for the Minister,

422
00:24:03,575 --> 00:24:06,135
I wouldn't have known
that other kinds of wood would not suffice,

423
00:24:07,495 --> 00:24:10,035
I didn't expect you to be this generous,

424
00:24:10,035 --> 00:24:12,895
You're willing to spend a great sum of money
just to ask about such a trivial matter,

425
00:24:29,015 --> 00:24:30,955
Given that, it really is quite a coincidence,

426
00:24:30,955 --> 00:24:32,335
Isn't it just coincidental?

427
00:24:33,215 --> 00:24:35,135
I wonder
if Prefect Wang is satisfied with my answer,

428
00:24:35,135 --> 00:24:36,215
I am enlightened,

429
00:24:36,215 --> 00:24:37,815
This money was offered voluntarily by you,

430
00:24:37,815 --> 00:24:39,895
It's not like I'm trying to swindle you,
just so you know,

431
00:24:39,895 --> 00:24:41,335
My questions were answered,
and I suppose it's not a loss after all,

432
00:24:41,335 --> 00:24:43,455
Even if you feel at a loss,
I'm not going to return the money,

433
00:24:43,455 --> 00:24:46,015
Certainly not!
It's worth every penny to see your true nature,

434
00:24:46,015 --> 00:24:47,415
The money was well spent,

435
00:24:47,415 --> 00:24:49,655
Are you sarcastically implying
my ignorance and superficiality?

436
00:24:49,655 --> 00:24:51,575
How could I dare,
My lady, your ideas are incredibly imaginative,

437
00:24:51,575 --> 00:24:52,895
We could only admire
and cannot hope to compare,

438
00:24:52,895 --> 00:24:53,935
Good to know,

439
00:24:53,935 --> 00:24:55,795
If there's anything else to ask,
please go ahead,

440
00:24:55,795 --> 00:24:58,935
The smell here is truly unpleasant,
and it's also very noisy,

441
00:24:58,935 --> 00:25:01,435
If one stays too long,
I fear it would be suffocating,

442
00:25:01,435 --> 00:25:03,435
Lady Liuli usually just gives advice,

443
00:25:03,435 --> 00:25:04,935
She doesn't want to see these people
do the heavy work,

444
00:25:05,455 --> 00:25:07,135
Why don't we call two craftsmen over

445
00:25:07,135 --> 00:25:08,735
and demonstrate directly
to the Minister how to do it?

446
00:25:08,735 --> 00:25:10,695
Great, Please go ahead and I won't see you out
as I still have things to do,

447
00:25:10,695 --> 00:25:12,535
It seems as if I liked to stay here, Let's go,

448
00:25:21,935 --> 00:25:23,835
- Despicable,
- Despicable,

449
00:25:23,835 --> 00:25:24,995
No worries, no worries,

450
00:25:24,995 --> 00:25:26,975
- Shrew,
- Shrew,

451
00:25:39,255 --> 00:25:40,535
Don't get so angry that it affects your health,

452
00:25:41,495 --> 00:25:43,035
You see, I originally thought this woman

453
00:25:43,035 --> 00:25:45,295
must be exceptionally smart
to come up with this idea,

454
00:25:45,295 --> 00:25:47,055
Who would have thought she's just a painter
at a fabric printing store?

455
00:25:49,415 --> 00:25:51,615
But it's good, after this,
we won't have to see her anymore,

456
00:26:03,323 --> 00:26:09,504
<i>[Protector-General's Mansion]</i>

457
00:26:10,415 --> 00:26:11,855
That medicine didn't have any effect at all,
did it?

458
00:26:11,855 --> 00:26:13,536
I told you, didn't I?

459
00:26:25,495 --> 00:26:29,855
Bai San,
it's better for you to be careful these days,

460
00:26:32,575 --> 00:26:36,015
Do not cause a bloody disaster
because of your speedy legs,

461
00:26:38,455 --> 00:26:40,015
Chancellor, you're making fun of me,

462
00:26:40,015 --> 00:26:42,815
I have been working on these legs
for over twenty years,

463
00:26:42,815 --> 00:26:44,975
They've never failed me,

464
00:26:45,575 --> 00:26:47,215
Senior Official,

465
00:26:47,215 --> 00:26:49,435
you may not know,

466
00:26:49,435 --> 00:26:51,475
Speaking of Sanlang's speed,

467
00:26:51,475 --> 00:26:53,335
Let alone our office,

468
00:26:53,335 --> 00:26:55,795
he's a prominent figure

469
00:26:55,795 --> 00:26:58,375
in the entire Xizhou,

470
00:27:04,295 --> 00:27:05,335
I indeed didn't misjudge,

471
00:27:06,375 --> 00:27:09,455
You'll certainly face a bloody disaster
within three days,

472
00:27:11,215 --> 00:27:13,255
If you don't believe it,

473
00:27:13,255 --> 00:27:15,095
why not have a bet between the two of us?

474
00:27:19,215 --> 00:27:20,855
How will we bet?

475
00:27:20,855 --> 00:27:22,095
If my words don't come true,

476
00:27:23,415 --> 00:27:24,495
as long as I'm on duty,

477
00:27:24,495 --> 00:27:27,055
you can receive assistant's allowance

478
00:27:27,055 --> 00:27:28,635
and do whatever you wish,

479
00:27:28,635 --> 00:27:29,975
I will definitely not interfere,

480
00:27:31,015 --> 00:27:32,495
If what I said comes true,

481
00:27:33,135 --> 00:27:34,875
then you must explain clearly

482
00:27:34,875 --> 00:27:37,055
how this bloody disaster come about,

483
00:27:37,855 --> 00:27:40,235
So that I could avoid suspicion
from others later on,

484
00:27:40,235 --> 00:27:41,575
in case someone accuse me
of foul play behind the scenes,

485
00:27:44,695 --> 00:27:45,935
Agreed,

486
00:27:45,935 --> 00:27:47,535
Then let those present bear witness,

487
00:27:48,135 --> 00:27:50,775
If I truly encounter a bloody disaster
in these few days,

488
00:27:51,775 --> 00:27:54,975
whether or not it is a setup by someone,

489
00:27:54,975 --> 00:28:00,135
I am all ears and obedient
to Senior Official Pei's orders,

490
00:28:01,135 --> 00:28:02,624
Good,

491
00:28:15,375 --> 00:28:18,235
Sanlang, you'd better be careful today,

492
00:28:18,235 --> 00:28:19,535
Although I don't believe

493
00:28:19,535 --> 00:28:21,275
there are any divine calculation techniques
in this world,

494
00:28:21,275 --> 00:28:23,335
however, since
Senior Official Pei dares to be so certain,

495
00:28:23,335 --> 00:28:25,075
I believe he must be somewhat confident,

496
00:28:25,075 --> 00:28:26,895
It's not all groundless speculation,

497
00:28:26,895 --> 00:28:29,015
Alarming talk is not worth worrying about,

498
00:28:29,015 --> 00:28:30,675
I'll go and return shortly,

499
00:28:30,675 --> 00:28:33,135
Keep watch here,

500
00:28:46,615 --> 00:28:48,015
Sanlang, be careful,

501
00:28:55,375 --> 00:28:58,415
S-Sanlang, what happened?

502
00:28:58,415 --> 00:28:59,455
Why are you so loud?

503
00:28:59,455 --> 00:29:01,735
It's too shady, They're all oil barrels,

504
00:29:02,495 --> 00:29:04,175
Sanlang, Sanlang,

505
00:29:05,655 --> 00:29:07,015
You think a little oil can trap me?

506
00:29:11,095 --> 00:29:13,215
What happened to Sanlang?

507
00:29:14,535 --> 00:29:21,015
Sanlang, Sanlang,

508
00:29:23,415 --> 00:29:27,295
Which bold thief dares to break into
Pei Mansion at night?

509
00:29:33,855 --> 00:29:36,815
People, come and surround this thief for me,

510
00:29:37,535 --> 00:29:38,976
Beat him up for me,

511
00:29:46,495 --> 00:29:49,455
What happened to Sanlang?

512
00:29:50,335 --> 00:29:51,616
Sanlang!

513
00:29:53,175 --> 00:29:54,415
Stop him, don't let him escape!

514
00:29:55,495 --> 00:29:56,735
Bold thief, where do you think you're going?

515
00:30:00,335 --> 00:30:01,408
San…Sanlang,

516
00:30:11,335 --> 00:30:12,448
Sanlang!

517
00:30:17,775 --> 00:30:19,855
Open the door, save me,

518
00:30:22,575 --> 00:30:23,615
Hansi!

519
00:30:25,495 --> 00:30:27,008
Hansi!

520
00:30:29,775 --> 00:30:31,136
Hansi!

521
00:30:35,175 --> 00:30:37,415
Sanlang is injured, Hansi, hurry and save him,

522
00:30:40,375 --> 00:30:41,856
He's still alive,

523
00:30:44,495 --> 00:30:47,455
