527
00:31:21,815 --> 00:31:24,735
I fell over at night,
and there's nothing to ask about,

528
00:31:25,535 --> 00:31:27,375
Is there really a divine calculation technique
in this world?

529
00:31:29,855 --> 00:31:31,136
Yes, there is,

530
00:31:31,136 --> 00:31:32,775
Yes,

531
00:31:36,215 --> 00:31:37,555
This is too frightening,

532
00:31:37,555 --> 00:31:40,615
Bai San, we have an agreement in advance,

533
00:31:41,335 --> 00:31:42,415
You need to explain to everyone,

534
00:31:42,935 --> 00:31:44,215
Where did you go last night?

535
00:31:44,215 --> 00:31:45,795
Why are you hurt?

536
00:31:45,795 --> 00:31:47,255
There's nothing good to say,

537
00:31:48,175 --> 00:31:49,415
I'm so injured,

538
00:31:50,215 --> 00:31:52,975
It's my own fault, and I can't blame others,

539
00:31:54,135 --> 00:31:55,335
Everyone, listen to me well,

540
00:31:55,935 --> 00:31:58,535
Senior Official Pei won this gamble,

541
00:31:59,495 --> 00:32:00,895
I, Bai San, am willing to admit defeat,

542
00:32:01,975 --> 00:32:06,415
From now on,
I'll only take Senior Official Pei's orders,

543
00:32:10,375 --> 00:32:14,175
Bai San, I don't think it's convenient for you
to carry out your duties these days,

544
00:32:14,815 --> 00:32:15,855
You should go home and rest well,

545
00:32:18,695 --> 00:32:19,815
Slow down, slow down, slow down,

546
00:32:20,655 --> 00:32:21,655
How did you get hurt?

547
00:32:25,615 --> 00:32:28,095
What kind of person do you think of me?

548
00:32:28,695 --> 00:32:31,255
Is it possible to unsay what has been said?

549
00:32:33,335 --> 00:32:35,815
With a minor injury like this?

550
00:32:36,575 --> 00:32:39,255
Even if my head falls off,
I have to finish my duties first,

551
00:32:39,255 --> 00:32:40,415
Then I'll go home and drop dead,

552
00:32:41,695 --> 00:32:42,895
That's not right,

553
00:32:43,775 --> 00:32:46,415
The bet was just a joke I made up with you,

554
00:32:47,055 --> 00:32:48,495
I was just kindly reminding you,

555
00:32:48,495 --> 00:32:49,975
Only got there
because one thing led to another,

556
00:32:50,495 --> 00:32:51,735
Why do you have to take it so seriously?

557
00:32:53,375 --> 00:32:55,875
You have to accept losing a bet
and repay your debts,

558
00:32:55,875 --> 00:32:58,415
I may be a lout,
but I will never be a scoundrel,

559
00:32:59,055 --> 00:33:00,192
All good,

560
00:33:02,215 --> 00:33:04,255
Since you say you'll obey me,

561
00:33:05,215 --> 00:33:08,055
then I now order you to go home and rest well,

562
00:33:08,735 --> 00:33:10,176
Are you listening or not?

563
00:33:15,655 --> 00:33:16,960
Gently,

564
00:33:23,975 --> 00:33:27,335
I'm afraid he won't be able to get out of bed
for a couple of months with his fall

565
00:33:31,215 --> 00:33:33,935
This Bai San really has no brains,

566
00:33:35,535 --> 00:33:37,575
I've warned him time and again to be careful,

567
00:33:40,735 --> 00:33:41,975
Alright, you may go now,

568
00:33:43,495 --> 00:33:44,864
Yes,

569
00:35:09,615 --> 00:35:12,615
By the way, you haven't been to
the Great Buddha Temple in the north, right?

570
00:35:13,375 --> 00:35:14,675
No, I haven't been there,

571
00:35:14,675 --> 00:35:16,775
But lately, I've often heard people mention it,

572
00:35:18,335 --> 00:35:19,655
Then you must go and see it,

573
00:35:21,015 --> 00:35:24,095
The Great Buddha Temple
is the most magnificent temple in Xizhou,

574
00:35:24,735 --> 00:35:27,215
Even compared to the Daci'en Temple
in Chang'an,

575
00:35:27,215 --> 00:35:28,375
it'll certainly not inferior,

576
00:35:29,375 --> 00:35:31,635
If we were to discuss it in terms of murals,

577
00:35:31,635 --> 00:35:33,615
it would be even more outstanding,

578
00:35:34,175 --> 00:35:37,495
<i>The entire Xizhou is not as big as a district
in Chang'an,</i>

579
00:35:38,055 --> 00:35:40,935
<i>Could there be a temple
that can compare to the Daci'en Temple?</i>

580
00:35:42,535 --> 00:35:43,935
Better than Daci'en Temple?

581
00:35:44,935 --> 00:35:46,975
Seeing is believing,

582
00:35:46,975 --> 00:35:49,975
I will take you to see it tomorrow, how's that?

583
00:35:49,975 --> 00:35:52,075
Great, I've wanted to go for a long time,

584
00:35:52,075 --> 00:35:53,095
No manners,

585
00:35:54,575 --> 00:35:56,235
There's not much rules in my place,

586
00:35:56,235 --> 00:35:58,095
This girl is lively and cute,

587
00:35:58,095 --> 00:35:59,615
She indeed suits my taste very much,

588
00:36:00,215 --> 00:36:01,655
Thank you very much, Lady Qu,

589
00:36:01,655 --> 00:36:04,855
