by distance,

618
00:37:50,155 --> 00:37:53,495
Now Xizhou is well governed
by the Protector-General,

619
00:37:53,495 --> 00:37:55,255
As the Chancellor, I have nothing to do
in my leisure time,

620
00:37:55,895 --> 00:37:57,855
If I can help Lady Liu find her cousin,

621
00:37:58,415 --> 00:37:59,695
