623
00:38:09,415 --> 00:38:10,855
I made a mistake, I made a mistake,

624
00:38:10,855 --> 00:38:12,355
Regret one step,

625
00:38:12,355 --> 00:38:13,696
Master,

626
00:38:14,975 --> 00:38:17,535
Master, Prefect Wang, Lady Liu is here,

627
00:38:17,535 --> 00:38:18,615
