635
00:38:40,635 --> 00:38:41,895
I'll take my leave,

636
00:38:45,095 --> 00:38:46,400
I'll take my leave,

637
00:38:52,535 --> 00:38:54,016
Prefect Wang,

638
00:38:55,175 --> 00:38:57,495
